name: Ext_R5_GuidanceResponse_result
title: Cross-version Extension for R5.GuidanceResponse.result for use in FHIR R4B
description: This cross-version extension represents GuidanceResponse.result from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/GuidanceResponse|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4B.

element.definition: The actions, if any, produced by the evaluation of the artifact.
element.comment: `GuidanceResponse.result` maps to R4B `GuidanceResponse.result`.
